               <msContents>
                  <summary change="#add-summary">
                     An incomplete <title>Dīvān-i Sanāʼī</title> by Ḥusayn ibn Muḥammad S̲anaʼī Mashhadī (d. ca. 1587), likely completed in the <date calendar="#Gregorian" notBefore="1700" notAfter="1850">18th to mid-19th century</date>.
                     Originally from Mashhad in Iran, he travelled to India where he attained favour under the Mughal ruler <persName key="person_3264079" role="pat" ref="https://viaf.org/viaf/3264079/">Akbar</persName> and also critically edited the poems of <persName key="person_90041360" ref="https://viaf.org/viaf/90041360/">Abū al-Fayz̤ ibn Mubārak</persName>, (d. 1595), pen named <addName type="penname">Fayz̤ī</addName>. 
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_579-item1">
                     <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/7152199212114281139/" key="person_7152199212114281139" >
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied">S̲anaʼī Mashhadī, Ḥusayn ibn Muḥammad, d. ca. 1587</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">ثنائي مشهدی، حسین بن محمد،</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">S̲anāʼī Mashhadī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="ar" type="alt">سنائی مشهدی</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20678">Dīvān | Sanāʼī Mashhadī</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20678" type="alt">Dīvān-i S̲anaʼī</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="">دیوان ثنائی</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa" type="basmalla"><locus from="1b" to="1b">:(folio 1b) برگ ۱ر</locus>
                        در روش خسن و ناز هست بسی خوش نما * غمزه بطرز ستم عشوه برنگ حفا</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa"><locus from="119b" to="119b">:(folio 119b) برگ ۱۱۹پ</locus>
                        شوقیت بجان رب در دریا را  * چو نیست بچشم خاک کسی کسی
                     </explicit>
                     <colophon>Colophon missing.</colophon>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>A prior version of this record mistakenly identified the author as <persName key="person_197073975" ref="https://viaf.org/viaf/197073975/">Ḥakīm Sanā'ī Ghaznavī</persName>; however, Michael Kerney notes the confusion and identifies the correct author in his handlist, 
                        <ref target="https://luna.manchester.ac.uk/luna/servlet/detail/Manchester~91~1~379072~126269?page=203">p. 201</ref>.</note>
                     <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_68-item1-item1">
